            <fr:title text="Being n-truncated is a proposition">Being <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001G.xml" title="n-truncated type" addr="//erct/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link> is a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link></fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001P.agda" type="external">erct-001P.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>It is a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link> that a given type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001G.xml" title="n-truncated type" addr="//erct/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="foreign-erct-jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="//erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>20</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>6501</fr:anchor><fr:addr type="machine">//erct/unstable/444</fr:addr><fr:route>foreign-erct-unstable-444.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  <fr:p>We proceed by induction on the <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001F.xml" title="Indexing of truncation levels" addr="//erct/erct-001F" type="local">truncation level</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
  <fr:ol><fr:li>When <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-2]]></fr:tex>, we recall from <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001N.xml" title="Being contractible is a proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001N" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-001N" /></fr:link> that being <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="//erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> is a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>.</fr:li>
    <fr:li>When <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-1]]></fr:tex>, we recall from <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001O.xml" title="Being a proposition is a proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001O" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-001O" /></fr:link> that
      being a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link> is a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>.</fr:li>
    <fr:li>For <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n \geq  0]]></fr:tex>, we assume by induction that being <html:span style="white-space: nowrap" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n-1]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span> is a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link> to prove that being <html:span style="white-space: nowrap" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span> is a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>. In other words, we must show that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}\mathsf {isTruncated}\,
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen n-1\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\,A]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>. By our inductive hypothesis, this is a dependent product of <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link> (<fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001B.xml" title="Dependent product of propositions" addr="//erct/erct-001B" type="local">Corollary <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-001B" /></fr:link>).</fr:li></fr:ol>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter>
